OL,3,CFire breaks out at a pub in Bangkok,
OL,4,Ckilling at least 27 people
OL,6,FA huge fire engulfed a pub in Bangkok
OL,7,Fearly on Monday morning, killing at
OL,8,Fleast 27 people before firefighters
OL,9,Fbrought the blaze under control,
OL,10,Fofficials said.
OL,12,FFootage shared online by first
OL,13,Fresponders shows a huge blaze raging
OL,14,Fand plumes coming out of the front
OL,15,Fdoor of the Na Ladprao pub in the
OL,16,Fnorthern part of the Thai capital.
OL,18,FPeople are seen trying to flee as
OL,19,Fthick black smoke billows into the
OL,20,Fsky. Rescuers said the fire was
OL,21,Freported around midnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
