OL,3,CFire breaks out at a pub in Bangkok,
OL,4,Ckilling at least 27 people
OL,6,FThailand's Prime Minister Anutin
OL,7,FCharnvirakul told reporters at the
OL,8,Fscene that 27 people died and that
OL,9,Fseveral of the injured have been taken
OL,10,Fto the hospital. He said the cause of
OL,11,Fthe fire is under investigation.
OL,13,FAnutin said a musician who was
OL,14,Fperforming at the pub told him that he
OL,15,Fsaw smoke coming out of a circuit
OL,16,Fbreaker near the stage before the
OL,17,Fpower went out, then an explosion was
OL,18,Fheard, and thick smoke quickly filled
OL,19,Fthe place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
