OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1783930924
OL,3,CFire breaks out at a pub in Bangkok,
OL,4,Ckilling at least 27 people
OL,6,FMany of the victims were found at the
OL,7,Frestrooms, at the back of the pub,
OL,8,FAnutin added.
OL,10,FFirefighters took about half an hour
OL,11,Fto bring the fire under control.
OL,12,FPhotos of the aftermath show charred
OL,13,Ftables and chairs and the damaged
OL,14,Finterior of the pub.
OL,16,FThailand has seen similar tragedies in
OL,17,Fthe past. In 2022, 14 people were
OL,18,Fkilled by a fire at a music pub in the
OL,19,Feastern part of the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
