OL,3,CFire breaks out at a pub in Bangkok,
OL,4,Ckilling at least 27 people
OL,6,FAnd more than a decade before that, 66
OL,7,Fpeople were killed and more than 200
OL,8,Fwere injured in a fire during a Jan.
OL,9,F1, 2009, New Year's Eve celebration at
OL,10,Fthe Santika nightclub in Thailand's
OL,11,Fcapital. That blaze was apparently
OL,12,Fsparked by an indoor fireworks display.
